{"type":"FeatureCollection","properties":{"name":"Appel à idées 2022  (données Octobre 2014 - fin Mai 2022)","short":"Appel à idées 2022"},"features":[{"type":"Feature","properties":{"image":{"src":"/data/images/CAUCASE.png","attribution":"Capture Google Earth"},"id":"urn:ogc:def:EOP:CNES::CAUCASE:","uuid":"9f63a391-3896-4333-ba25-7a119bc45156","link":"https://www.poleterresolide.fr/acces-aux-donnees/catalogue/#/metadata/9f63a391-3896-4333-ba25-7a119bc45156","name":"Caucase","location":"Caucase","description":"Le projet a pour objectif de mieux comprendre comment se distribue la déformation associée à la convergence entre l’Arabie et l’Eurasie dans la région du Caucase, où différentes failles inverses et décrochantes, à fort alea sismique, co-existent. Il devrait permettre de proposer un modèle cinématique et sismo-tectonique régional et une quantification, en particulier, des mouvements verticaux. Des objectifs complémentaires incluent le suivi de volcans de boue en Azerbaïdjan, aux éruptions fréquentes, ou de la déformation d’origine anthropique.","theme":["Dynamique des Réservoirs d’Hydrocarbure","Tectonique","Volcans de boue"],"leaders":["F. Masson (ITES)"],"popup":"fmt-under","width":110},"geometry":{"type":"Polygon","coordinates":[[[43.83611383915,41.2899935302879],[44.404433433441916,39.20552583029565],[44.1207876487909,37.8664461387919],[44.79398661964525,37.776732872555684],[45.0426610488171,36.8646513243758],[47.8797819484448,37.2856764168505],[47.44298157377281,39.46299108315667],[48.3085000774528,42.6515648797287],[45.2221182932488,43.0657812935124],[44.87574666866208,41.430575578159015],[43.83611383915,41.2899935302879]]]}},{"type":"Feature","properties":{"image":{"src":"/data/images/CHILI.png","attribution":"Capture Google Earth"},"id":"urn:ogc:def:EOP:CNES::CHILI:","uuid":"9a7c359f-fa6b-4a79-b639-826f3dd16f96","link":"https://www.poleterresolide.fr/acces-aux-donnees/catalogue/#/metadata/9a7c359f-fa6b-4a79-b639-826f3dd16f96","name":"Centre Chili","location":"Centre Chili",
"marker": { "lat": -27.44979032978423, "lng": -65.8367047827051 },
"description":"Le projet vise à quantifier les déformations associées à la subduction andine dans la région du Chili central, avec pour objectifs principaux de : \n(1) contraindre la cinématique et le couplage intersismique de l’interface de subduction et des failles crustales, au front et à l’intérieur de la chaîne des Andes,\n(2) analyser les déformations co- et post-sismiques lors des différentes crises sismiques et les épisodes de glissements lents,\n(3) faire le lien entre cycle sismique et construction des reliefs,\n(4) suivre le fonctionnement des volcans de l’arc andin.  Un autre objectif est de caractériser les épisodes d’érosion pendant les évènements climatiques extrêmes dans le Désert d’Atacama.","theme":["Tectonique","Volcanisme","Erosion"],"leaders":["A. Socquet (ISTerre)"],"width":110},"geometry":{"type":"Polygon","coordinates":[[[-74.2332,-39.9077],[-73.75239541392116,-40.0236782625422],[-73.876,-40.398],[-72.84386679126226,-40.66980875844473],[-72.5607,-41.5021],[-71.00179600691064,-41.15491181357676],[-70.8078,-41.206],[-70.77811734016795,-41.10509566646814],[-70.6816,-41.0836],[-70.73204820582663,-40.948486544394754],[-70.4158398484258,-39.873556139192864],[-69.3723,-39.61],[-69.91058112729887,-38.15596092350317],[-69.29330372440384,-36.05756525088403],[-68.663,-35.919],[-68.98266248947573,-35.0015599280696],[-68.93704633776225,-34.84649069192361],[-66.6424,-35.4487],[-66.28511719381315,-34.16885639639233],[-64.3488,-34.6917],[-63.052319158853244,-30.40941323156016],[-62.4964,-30.2666],[-62.74968031875061,-29.409794679973118],[-62.1614,-27.4667],[-63.4121934098452,-27.168622749057274],[-63.88470423698819,-25.57019697139139],[-61.6776,-17.664],[-64.2116,-17.1137],[-64.22344299400261,-17.15357133763205],[-64.2547,-17.0366],[-64.9732,-17.1826],[-64.96896559646133,-17.198146939162378],[-64.99070836082083,-17.19163931997039],[-65.1082,-16.7321],[-65.89995431316744,-16.884957097525277],[-66.0236,-16.4154],[-66.8192,-16.5603],[-66.46508940241314,-17.954941703897347],[-68.8700373407479,-25.23803951872108],[-69.29049268013418,-25.336100875900016],[-69.3218,-25.3299],[-69.32673708393784,-25.344554033927018],[-69.41725735627489,-25.36566576667498],[-69.3671,-25.2083],[-70.3988,-25.0265],[-70.58774733669868,-25.63865513151988],[-70.5948,-25.6403],[-70.59162161539605,-25.65120709243646],[-70.94019763160375,-26.780530219052338],[-72.2605,-27.1568],[-71.63402519183421,-29.02840578483668],[-72.04921487357974,-30.373545116649233],[-73.2244,-30.6742],[-72.24281786263927,-33.99993587530702],[-72.60344672976917,-35.0703385098402],[-73.8379,-35.4429],[-73.36480343236087,-36.78713669478717],[-74.114,-36.9366],[-73.67094487167209,-38.238839225121424],[-74.2332,-39.9077]]]}},{"type":"Feature","properties":{"image":{"src":"/data/images/MOZAMBIQUE.png","attribution":"Capture Google Earth"},"id":"urn:ogc:def:EOP:CNES::MOZAMBIQUE:","uuid":"a16a5be8-67b4-428e-85bc-654000e92c22","link":"https://www.poleterresolide.fr/acces-aux-donnees/catalogue/#/metadata/a16a5be8-67b4-428e-85bc-654000e92c22","name":"Mozambique","location":"Mozambique","description":"Ce projet s’intéresse à la partie sud du rift est-africain dans la région du Mozambique. Cette zone de frontière de plaques naissante, à faible taux d’extension, a connu plusieurs séismes de Mw> 5 depuis le 20ème siècle. Le projet a pour objectif d’extraire le signal tectonique des séries temporelles InSAR afin de mieux caractériser les structures actives (failles normales) et leur cinématique, encore très mal contraintes.","theme":["Tectonique"],"leaders":["M. de Michele (BRGM)","A. Fuenzalida (BRGM)"],"width":110},"geometry":{"type":"Polygon","coordinates":[[[31.20337541861496,-22.64956511932384],[33.68375397449336,-22.76881841439276],[33.701348752646865,-22.69589201767231],[35.76615703544824,-22.76694361814591],[37.20953218513935,-16.70824228050375],[34.91317489936632,-16.57198403517489],[34.90973480326237,-16.585408147981408],[32.85570491152644,-16.47947770789601],[31.20337541861496,-22.64956511932384]]]}},{"type":"Feature","properties":{"image":{"src":"/data/images/MEXIQUE.png","attribution":"Capture Google Earth"},"id":"urn:ogc:def:EOP:CNES::MEXIQUE:","uuid":"91fad8f8-ee8e-4c18-acc1-45c8f8732d8c","link":"https://www.poleterresolide.fr/acces-aux-donnees/catalogue/#/metadata/91fad8f8-ee8e-4c18-acc1-45c8f8732d8c","name":"Sud Mexique","location":"Sud Mexique",
"marker":{ "lat": 18.47960905583198, "lng": -98.24955220645346 },
"description":"Un premier objectif de ce projet est de contraindre le couplage intersismique le long de l’interface de subduction Mexicaine et ses variations temporelles; il s’agit de mieux quantifier la répartition entre glissements sismiques et asismiques (séismes lents) pour mieux estimer le potentiel sismique de cette zone de subduction. Un second objectif est d’étudier les déformations crustales, de la plaque supérieure, le long de la ceinture volcanique trans-mexicaine : déformations d’origine tectonique, liées aux failles crustales, et volcanique, ou déformations d’origine anthropique (subsidence des bassins sédimentaires en relation avec la surexploitation des aquifères).","theme":["Hydrologie","Tectonique","Volcanisme"],"leaders":["E. Pathier (ISTerre)"],"popup":"fmt-under","width":110},"geometry":{"type":"Polygon","coordinates":[[[-105.9001135039858,21.85618811767324],[-105.43401575653732,19.756875278060477],[-105.6249099257628,18.59676668596357],[-105.15999706337351,18.52269003687074],[-104.9754273451039,17.69138462617479],[-103.54008258237629,17.901078771838137],[-103.0078810961002,17.80016184159157],[-102.7842894361431,16.68842703802721],[-100.77897186398857,16.977844038770943],[-100.5761985862717,15.92693386334439],[-98.77137175740559,16.118101517787675],[-98.58768145578925,16.08623682331408],[-98.43789805666937,15.34391898240717],[-96.64327259280678,15.581699937924487],[-95.71116925111413,15.42501007429204],[-95.66161169887931,15.655849134675954],[-95.49521374159832,15.678906791379616],[-93.70225859864945,15.30566580994455],[-93.00907494408884,18.32381090049136],[-94.53358541901498,18.638806925798548],[-94.76498704822983,19.84990293687342],[-96.46539079892658,19.626037394377242],[-96.82699784570158,19.687796886715223],[-96.8615423900729,19.858665767091676],[-96.85001452488356,19.91686001278067],[-96.87415016151914,19.921028025163615],[-97.00954021389725,20.59071254655411],[-98.97632583546952,20.390659806037455],[-99.13702067886922,21.22551125202961],[-101.11543235816384,20.95907842562548],[-101.205510857219,20.97545464798489],[-101.3742794781708,21.82557530772111],[-103.35635365542764,21.559552746930684],[-103.4643225594924,22.11386221067441],[-105.9001135039858,21.85618811767324]]]}},{"type":"Feature","properties":{"image":{"src":"/data/images/TIBETHIM.png","attribution":"Capture Google Earth"},"id":"urn:ogc:def:EOP:CNES::TIBETHIM:","uuid":"45808b4c-e380-4b1d-96cb-25803539183e","link":"https://www.poleterresolide.fr/acces-aux-donnees/catalogue/#/metadata/45808b4c-e380-4b1d-96cb-25803539183e","name":"Himalaya et Ouest Tibet","location":"Himalaya et Ouest Tibet",
"marker":{ "lat": 32.62087018318113, "lng": 87.50015076595578 },
"description":"Ce projet vient compléter le projet Tibet Est de l'AI FLATSIM 1, avec des objectifs variés de quantification des déformations tectoniques associées à la convergence Inde-Asie, depuis le front Himalayen et sur l'ensemble du plateau tibétain, de caractérisation de la rhéologie de la lithosphère et des processus hydrologiques, gravitaires, ou liés à la cryosphère. Les liens éventuels entre cycle sismique, forçages externes et construction des reliefs seront explorés. Des aspects plus méthodologiques comme le  référencement quasi-absolu des mesures InSAR seront également abordés.","theme":["Tectonique","Aléa Gravitaire","Glaciers","Hydrologie","Permafrost"],"leaders":["M.-P. Doin (ISTerre)","C. Lasserre (LGLTPE)","R. Jolivet (Laboratoire de Géologie","ENS Paris)"],"popup":"fmt-under","width":110},"geometry":{"type":"Polygon","coordinates":[[[76.49593706874006,34.707984800886],[77.54802626162171,29.717582206447652],[77.49275148087551,29.38272164503712],[77.62232396090893,29.365163957317883],[77.73623088123608,28.8248662386728],[79.38511228273288,29.003907526686813],[79.27653535365111,28.43162607211715],[79.92666507015433,28.335273752925495],[79.99642080034728,28.01032416397006],[81.3509826910845,28.124183100462634],[81.38814497781605,28.1186754726429],[81.3644051562035,27.97707340899438],[82.16050022242902,27.822975079438855],[82.31811814674856,27.14373076121879],[83.54494617123338,27.26588600586197],[84.30204782892268,27.12272447893988],[84.41117227544233,26.5627951687343],[86.4753160100861,26.655383691433823],[86.53491300840844,26.369726012497],[88.45513343089729,26.57502335915171],[88.60882696443836,26.557096707914923],[88.62781122633587,26.47543840249172],[89.09064254171277,26.500898248453115],[89.77436712803886,26.42114933567397],[89.79694142716066,26.539750979953283],[90.49285823068628,26.578032604448115],[90.6190516046108,26.564200596235793],[90.62845625202148,26.52392176712441],[90.84400851061969,26.53954315444971],[91.77093137087235,26.43794348866319],[91.80517613390118,26.609200377368467],[92.52893150709706,26.661651987418786],[93.79647121066058,26.48305818929206],[94.6702,30.5403],[92.35010256788166,30.810210140280677],[92.27870658069821,31.13498159261055],[92.24389304329549,31.130107777203012],[91.46874460401466,34.5312156801142],[91.63250723032952,35.24440518848677],[91.57094322462558,35.253302149746936],[92.64516777846059,39.42181767654652],[89.78111966320203,39.72350150686384],[89.72220776441128,39.45925158067263],[88.70892468811086,39.33678221600357],[87.70751688546923,39.44229414321393],[87.55416067530093,38.80212544753003],[85.72294935712127,38.53174720726602],[86.3969713138836,35.874575195154634],[85.2939332161285,35.7132290928313],[85.29032392607787,35.73152623582564],[85.21816737383931,35.720677722750864],[84.79794871363168,35.77751016193056],[84.77294719051531,35.65374025373246],[83.2532949829321,35.42526527354535],[83.22705385367223,35.56019810167167],[80.4801258343178,35.10575638925769],[80.48150190153395,35.099813846487315],[79.20729760495712,34.93408539223224],[79.2056,34.9427],[76.49593706874006,34.707984800886]]]}},{"type":"Feature","properties":{"image":{"src":"/data/images/LEVANT.png","attribution":"Capture Google Earth"},"id":"urn:ogc:def:EOP:CNES::LEVANT:","uuid":"e50bc742-1079-4f61-8dea-a49cdc55e4b7","link":"https://www.poleterresolide.fr/acces-aux-donnees/catalogue/#/metadata/e50bc742-1079-4f61-8dea-a49cdc55e4b7","name":"Levant","location":"Levant","description":"L’objectif principal du projet est d’analyser la distribution du couplage (i.e. la segmentation en zones bloquées ou en glissement asismique) le long du système de failles actives du Levant, au regard des séquences de séismes historiques et des propriétés physiques des failles, à des fins d’amélioration de l’estimation de l’alea sismique. Le projet inclut également l’étude de processus hydrologiques et de leurs forçages (anthropiques notamment, liés à la gestion des ressources en eau), ou gravitaires (glissements de terrain et facteurs contrôlant leur déclenchement et leur vitesse).","theme":["Alea gravitaire et anthropique","Hydrologie","Tectonique"],"leaders":["S. Michel (Laboratoire de Géologie","ENS Paris)"],"popup":"fmt-under","width":110},"geometry":{"type":"Polygon","coordinates":[[[31.8760874258152,28.0900869520305],[32.65871767337764,27.966061246031604],[32.7743445397849,27.4501029092911],[34.363042784640975,27.69574167403976],[36.4238394058572,27.3576274980155],[36.648404006947466,28.35425500793752],[37.2776185018302,28.4550796340691],[36.9925441016523,29.88156378227169],[37.23868904047681,30.973965773812523],[38.7750314470572,31.2016839042792],[38.09787329578303,34.700851649960775],[38.2490843042986,35.340190524873876],[39.9795696943692,35.592371364122],[39.1186169363457,39.528714202978],[37.11300725131656,39.2803267277591],[37.1079522537927,39.3029541992994],[36.42404151065596,39.20263468403824],[34.1545714659046,39.5193573308337],[33.2197465523517,34.8942361148249],[35.22504793299303,34.63670500787568],[35.2144091086576,34.58513116716884],[33.2918670063887,34.3086849418805],[33.696425429210635,32.533169038208925],[32.7555044743829,32.6619188769309],[32.513662225686794,31.404651787124802],[31.9093486220907,31.3099485390157],[32.22473557756756,29.90260668124771],[31.8760874258152,28.0900869520305]]]}},{"type":"Feature","properties":{"image":{"src":"/data/images/MAGHREB.png","attribution":"Capture Google Earth"},"id":"urn:ogc:def:EOP:CNES::MAGHREB:","uuid":"e3af66f8-e5dc-48bd-8833-61cb27dc8492","link":"https://www.poleterresolide.fr/acces-aux-donnees/catalogue/#/metadata/e3af66f8-e5dc-48bd-8833-61cb27dc8492","name":"Maghreb","location":"Maghreb",
"marker":{ "lat": 33.8339199536547, "lng": 0.7343338763908271 },
"description":"Ce projet vise principalement à quantifier la déformation d’origine tectonique sur l’ensemble du Maghreb, dans la zone de convergence Afrique/Eurasie. Il s’agit en particulier d’estimer la distribution spatiale et l’évolution temporelle de la déformation intersismique ou associée aux séismes récents sur les failles actives, depuis les côtes jusqu’à la plateforme saharienne. Des thématiques secondaires (glissements de terrain, subsidence du littoral, mouvement de dunes au Sahara, déformations d’origine anthropique associées aux grands ouvrages, à l’extraction des ressources naturelles, à l’agriculture…) seront également abordées.","theme":["Aléa Gravitaire","Tectonique","Hydrologie","Dynamique des Réservoirs d’Hydrocarbure"],"leaders":["C. Doubre (ITES)"],"popup":"fmt-under","width":110},"geometry":{"type":"Polygon","coordinates":[[[-11.540271192077,32.468893073021],[-10.0935174400771,26.1136060274984],[-7.59044625362264,26.5040423450437],[-7.789786048211599,27.499644801175517],[-5.80005505775587,27.8197592507441],[-5.998878317199276,28.8345192661869],[-3.98682329552808,29.1517878620818],[-4.1019272685958805,29.731401360947572],[-2.7211424498482657,29.94568554145207],[-2.72091376252843,29.9446944932608],[-2.425173688581881,29.991616973056615],[-2.10717996200365,30.0409664619706],[-2.1073934801590966,30.042036367392477],[-0.104188168569822,30.3598673583217],[-0.20414467181887047,30.858122525620864],[1.78998695807073,31.1618830559849],[1.7169419770706051,31.526386295251665],[3.72302302443349,31.8322084409336],[3.597079360172028,32.4569670793188],[5.58824599073073,32.7728286599051],[5.5440867526785365,32.991628115532556],[6.814462512481883,33.17634150494017],[6.878201,32.905281],[8.853485843955534,33.20209014820681],[8.99546797811469,32.6006551215955],[11.6959679955817,33.0041387144138],[10.7832332661967,37.5511637664897],[8.781563550664096,37.27313506156111],[8.75137019775099,37.4238203783134],[6.7526391777663655,37.14064959264853],[6.71387598692983,37.3386187458494],[4.723409359900168,37.057906763126795],[4.72318645321901,37.05901121743],[1.88588866783406,36.65509236723],[1.8859218547464267,36.65495157886576],[-0.105979687952991,36.372798938051],[-0.0712920223302074,36.2265975881916],[-2.0602418059632,35.94205372456],[-1.9893168858641601,35.640061313913186],[-3.1894310425315275,35.463954012914805],[-3.338889,36.212864],[-5.332202754061988,35.92653311612828],[-5.33325196207988,35.9318164709429],[-8.12785506072472,35.5204460143684],[-7.725432874349526,33.7664355731304],[-9.704005,33.471752],[-9.547291672532547,32.773716362736714],[-11.540271192077,32.468893073021]]]}},{"type":"Feature","properties":{"image":{"src":"/data/images/MAKRAN.png","attribution":"Capture Google Earth"},"id":"urn:ogc:def:EOP:CNES::MAKRAN:","uuid":"d569dbcc-0a13-4f60-a116-e4c54c1bf205","link":"https://www.poleterresolide.fr/acces-aux-donnees/catalogue/#/metadata/d569dbcc-0a13-4f60-a116-e4c54c1bf205","name":"Makran","location":"Makran","description":"Le projet vise à analyser le partitionnement de la déformation le long de la marge active du Makran, zone de convergence entre l'Arabie et l'Eurasie. Cette région est marquée par de grandes zones de chevauchements et un comportement sismique variable latéralement (grands séismes à l’est, sismicité plus modérée à l’ouest). Le mode d’accumulation de la déformation au travers des structures tectoniques actives sera analysé au regard des connaissances sur la structure lithosphérique et la géologie, afin de mieux contraindre l’alea sismique et l’histoire géodynamique de la région.","theme":["Tectonique"],"leaders":["S. Chevrot (GET)","D. Remy (GET)"],"popup":"fmt-under","width":110},"geometry":{"type":"Polygon","coordinates":[[[56.2057693224771,25.8717871414151],[57.82121757464902,25.78606277279627],[58.01785616931966,24.88745685460797],[59.90657010037995,25.208982561779546],[60.64642238818637,25.10300545502334],[61.48976638294062,29.0104814622753],[59.73309569387755,29.28335652477344],[59.60643017577807,29.92307745160581],[57.00633362123747,29.50994792565148],[57.0379684438826,29.36538200817549],[56.835437479544,29.3713172630271],[56.2057693224771,25.8717871414151]]]}},{"type":"Feature","properties":{"image":{"src":"/data/images/TIANSHAN.png","attribution":"Capture Google Earth"},"id":"urn:ogc:def:EOP:CNES::TIANSHAN:","uuid":"136a5eab-a672-406e-8876-d5a87fb38acb","link":"https://www.poleterresolide.fr/acces-aux-donnees/catalogue/#/metadata/136a5eab-a672-406e-8876-d5a87fb38acb","name":"Tian Shan","location":"Tian Shan","description":"L’objectif du projet est d’analyser la déformation au travers de la chaîne de montagne intracontinentale du Tianshan, liée à la collision Inde/Asie. Il s’agit en particulier \n(1) de quantifier le partitionnement de la déformation entre failles inverses et failles décrochantes, \n(2) de mieux comprendre le fonctionnement des plis et chevauchements au cours du cycle sismique, dans le piémont et au coeur de la chaîne, \nEt enfin (3) de documenter les phénomènes de versants à l’échelle régionale (mouvements gravitaires, déformations liées au gel-dégel du pergélisol, solifluxion.), en lien avec la sismicité, et le changement climatique.","theme":["Permafrost","Tectonique","Aléa Gravitaire"],"leaders":["M. Rizza (CEREGE)"],"popup":"fmt-under","width":110},"geometry":{"type":"Polygon","coordinates":[[[69.26,40.1],[71.05648027112079,39.855580915493775],[71.28,39.04],[73.28312349726777,39.316292896174865],[73.37,39],[75.32773083531049,39.26510938394829],[75.34,39.22],[75.64050980392157,39.26027450980392],[76.15,39.19],[76.18959763602449,39.33386360070431],[78.25,39.61],[78.24611587913334,39.62779738964277],[80.24,39.9],[79.40082028244862,43.774107868996566],[79.76,45.05],[79.10710157051534,45.13007244889906],[78.91,46.04],[75.87896040937248,45.6762752491247],[75.98,46.05],[72.69,46.45],[72.49002189901661,45.52679282703909],[69.6,45.17],[70.02042174723856,43.63596112465929],[69.26,40.1]]]}}]}
